          <div class="agent-flow-legend"><span><i></i>蓝线：主 Agent 下发子任务 / 发起工具调用</span><span class="is-return"><i></i>绿虚线：输入、结果与摘要返回主 Agent</span></div>
          <div class="agent-core"><span class="agent-core-role">主 Agent</span><b id="agent-core-mode">OBSERVE</b><small id="agent-core-detail">读取 · 决策 · 调用 · 验证</small></div>
          <div class="graph-node agent-worker worker-planner" data-start="0.03" data-end="0.30"><span>INPUT → MAIN</span><b>四类任务输入</b><small>Goal · Context · Constraints · Done when</small></div>
          <div class="graph-node agent-worker worker-context" data-start="0.25" data-end="0.62"><span>OPTIONAL CHILD</span><b>探索子 Agent</b><small>主 Agent 委派只读探索 · 摘要返回</small></div>
          <div class="graph-node agent-worker worker-builder" data-start="0.38" data-end="0.76"><span>MAIN ACTION</span><b>主 Agent 实施</b><small>读取工具结果 · 统一修改项目</small></div>
          <div class="graph-node agent-worker worker-reviewer" data-start="0.77" data-end="0.98"><span>OPTIONAL CHILD</span><b>审查子 Agent</b><small>独立运行检查 · 证据返回</small></div>
          <div class="graph-node capability-node node-skill" data-start="0.13" data-end="0.38"><b>Skill</b><small>主 Agent 按需加载的任务方法</small></div>
          <div class="graph-node capability-node node-mcp" data-start="0.51" data-end="0.68"><b>MCP Connector</b><small>把外部能力提供为标准工具</small></div>
          <div class="graph-node capability-node node-files" data-start="0.51" data-end="0.68"><b>File Tool</b><small>主 Agent 调用 · 读取或修改文件</small></div>
          <div class="graph-node capability-node node-terminal" data-start="0.55" data-end="0.76"><b>Terminal Tool</b><small>主 Agent 调用 · 构建、测试、诊断</small></div>
          <div class="graph-node capability-node node-browser" data-start="0.77" data-end="0.90"><b>Browser Tool</b><small>主 Agent 调用 · 检查真实页面</small></div>
          <div class="graph-node capability-node node-test" data-start="0.80" data-end="0.98"><b>Done Check</b><small>用完成标准判断修正或交付</small></div>
        </div>
        <div class="agent-log">
          <div class="agent-event"><span>01</span><div><b>接收目标、上下文、约束和完成标准</b><small>这些输入是主 Agent 每一步判断的依据</small></div><em>等待</em></div>
          <div class="agent-event"><span>02</span><div><b>读取项目文件、规则与当前状态</b><small>先观察现场，避免脱离现有代码直接生成</small></div><em>等待</em></div>
          <div class="agent-event"><span>03</span><div><b>按需加载与任务匹配的 Skill</b><small>Skill 提供做法和检查流程，不替 Agent 自主决策</small></div><em>等待</em></div>
          <div class="agent-event"><span>04</span><div><b>判断单 Agent 是否足够</b><small>只有独立、可并行、可验收的工作才委派子 Agent</small></div><em>等待</em></div>
          <div class="agent-event"><span>05</span><div><b>选择并调用本地工具或 MCP 工具</b><small>Agent 发出请求；工具执行动作并返回结果</small></div><em>等待</em></div>
          <div class="agent-event"><span>06</span><div><b>读取工具结果与子 Agent 摘要</b><small>新信息进入当前 Context，主 Agent 统一实施和整合</small></div><em>等待</em></div>
          <div class="agent-event"><span>07</span><div><b>对照完成标准运行验证</b><small>构建、测试和页面检查未通过就继续修正</small></div><em>等待</em></div>
          <div class="agent-event"><span>08</span><div><b>交付结果，或向用户请求必要决策</b><small>说明改动、验证证据、剩余风险与下一步</small></div><em>等待</em></div>
        </div>
        <div class="build-meter"><div id="build-meter-fill"></div></div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="work-panel runtime-panel">
      <div class="work-panel__head"><span>实时调用 / TOOL TRACE</span><span>03</span></div>
      <div class="work-panel__body runtime-body">
        <div class="active-call-card">
          <div class="active-call__top"><span id="active-call-kind">TASK CONTEXT</span><em id="active-call-status">运行中</em></div>
          <b id="active-call-title">读取任务与项目现场</b>
          <div class="call-io"><span>输入</span><code id="active-call-request">Goal · Context · Constraints · Done when</code></div>
          <div class="call-io response"><span>返回</span><code id="active-call-response">等待项目内容与规则读取完成</code></div>
        </div>
        <div class="runtime-group">
          <h3>调用队列</h3>
          <div class="runtime-call"><span class="call-dot"></span><div><b>读取仓库与项目规则</b><small>FILE TOOL · read project + AGENTS.md</small></div><em>待命</em></div>
          <div class="runtime-call"><span class="call-dot"></span><div><b>加载相关 Skill</b><small>SKILL · reusable instructions + checks</small></div><em>待命</em></div>
          <div class="runtime-call"><span class="call-dot"></span><div><b>可选：委派独立探索</b><small>SUBAGENT · scoped task → summary</small></div><em>待命</em></div>
          <div class="runtime-call"><span class="call-dot"></span><div><b>读取并修改项目文件</b><small>FILE TOOL · read / patch / write</small></div><em>待命</em></div>
          <div class="runtime-call"><span class="call-dot"></span><div><b>按需查询外部资料</b><small>MCP TOOL · request → external result</small></div><em>待命</em></div>
          <div class="runtime-call"><span class="call-dot"></span><div><b>运行构建与页面检查</b><small>TERMINAL + BROWSER · verify behavior</small></div><em>待命</em></div>
          <div class="runtime-call"><span class="call-dot"></span><div><b>读取结果并对照完成标准</b><small>CONTEXT · outputs → next decision</small></div><em>待命</em></div>
          <div class="runtime-call"><span class="call-dot"></span><div><b>汇总改动、证据与风险</b><small>FINAL · deliver or ask user</small></div><em>待命</em></div>
        </div>
        <div class="runtime-group artifacts-group">
          <h3>工作产物</h3>
          <div class="artifact-item"><span>main.js</span><em>等待创建</em></div>
          <div class="artifact-item"><span>template.html</span><em>等待创建</em></div>
          <div class="artifact-item"><span>preview.png</span><em>等待采集</em></div>
          <div class="artifact-item"><span>test-report.json</span><em>等待验证</em></div>
        </div>
        <div class="delivery-check"><span>最终交付状态</span><b id="final-check">运行中</b></div>
      </div>
    </article>
